家啦哈哈。举个例子，我男朋友对护肤品的认知因为他们办公室女生的普及 一直停留在 la mer 鱼子酱这些，对包也都是需要配货的级别。我用的就比较随便。 我们从小相识，他可能觉得我一直没受过什么苦，所以和他一起后，他就一直想给我最好的。之前我有说不用给我买东西，他反而觉得我跟他生分客气，还问我哪有女生不爱包。哈哈哈我就笑了啊，爱是真爱啊，但我能看清比包更珍贵的东西。"},"attached_info":"Cj4ImtW36Oq96rdLEAMaCDcyMzk5MTcyIL7284sGMAA4OEAtcgk0OTU1MzE5MTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"49 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"46_1636158251.2322736","card_id":"Q_19897012","target":{"id":19897012,"title":"科学研究的最终目标和目的是什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/19897012","type":"question","created":1319921797,"answer_count":85,"follower_count":282,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2232,2725,6280,13758,20858],"comment_count":5,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CjwImtW36Oq96rdLEAMaBjEzODgzOSCF0bH1BDAFOJoCQC5yCDE5ODk3MDEyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"48 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-47f58c683d05d3a23e08e7c354cf3b5d_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"47_1636158251.2327068","card_id":"Q_496515781","target":{"id":496515781,"title":"想参加 23 年跨专业考研，应该怎么开始呢？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/496515781","type":"question","created":1635993701,"answer_count":42,"follower_count":117,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4287,17566,25992,33814,62421],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"本科的专业比较不好就业，想换个好就业的专业读研究生，不知道跨专业考研该选什么专业，需要怎么准备？"},"attached_info":"Cj4ImtW36Oq96rdLEAMaCDcyNjE3OTQ4IOWQjYwGMAA4dUAvcgk0OTY1MTU3ODF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"48 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v